        <li><strong>Documentation requirements:</strong> Same record keeping</li>
        <li><strong>Audit process:</strong> Similar procedures</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Financing Rules Update</h2>

      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <thead>
          <tr style="background: #D4A574; color: white;">
            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #B8956A;">Factor</th>
            <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #B8956A;">2026 Status</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Down Payment Rules</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd;">No law change - Banks still require 10-20%</td>
          </tr>
