            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Banks still restrict to 5 years</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Capital Allowance</strong></td>
            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #E8F5E9;">Same for all - Bank or Ing Heng</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Ing Heng Credit: Unchanged Benefits</h2>

      <p>Despite tax law changes, our benefits remain:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>0% down payment:</strong> Still available</li>
