        <li><strong>Review publications:</strong> Tax guides and updates</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Planning for 2026</h2>

      <h3>Early Year Planning</h3>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Review new rules:</strong> January-February</li>
        <li><strong>Adjust strategy:</strong> Based on changes</li>
        <li><strong>Buy early:</strong> If beneficial rules change</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Ongoing Monitoring</h3>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Watch for updates:</strong> Throughout the year</li>
        <li><strong>Adjust purchases:</strong> As rules evolve</li>
        <li><strong>Maximize benefits:</strong> Under new rules</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>0% Down Payment in 2026</h2>

      <p>Our 0% down payment advantage continues:</p>

      <ul>
